headline: Tariff Deals Spark Unusual Options Trading in Carrier Global Corp Stock
summary: Carrier Global Corp stock is up on news that the Trump Administration has made several Asian trade and tariff deals. That has sparked unusual out-of-the-money CARR put options trading, signaling investor interest in the stock.
